    "description": "<p>ALSTERN MARINE &amp; OFFSHORE PTE. LTD.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Alstern Marine &amp; Offshore Pte Ltd &nbsp;was founded in 2011. We are headquartered in Singapore with regional offices in Hong Kong and Indonesia.</p>\n<p>Our business scope involved distributing of Sealxpert pipeline maintenance, repair &amp; overhaul products to customers in the Oil &amp; Gas, Petrochemical, Chemical, Power, Water Utilities and Facilities Management Industries. Currently our products are distributed to more than 35 countries worldwide in Asia, Middle East, Europe, America and Australia.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
